-- Conversion to and from Pointwise (proto-reflexivity)
 
  fromPointwise : Pointwise R ‚áí Sublist R
  fromPointwise []       = []
  fromPointwise (p ‚à∑ ps) = p ‚à∑ fromPointwise ps
 
  toPointwise : length as ‚â° length bs ‚Üí
                Sublist R as bs ‚Üí Pointwise R as bs

  toPointwise {bs = b ‚à∑ bs} eq (b ‚à∑ ≥ rs) =
    contradiction (s‚â§s (length-mono-‚â§ rs)) (‚Ñï.<-irrefl eq)

-- Various functions' outputs are sublists
 
-- These lemmas are generalisations of results of the form `f xs ‚äÜ xs`.
-- (where _‚äÜ_ stands for Sublist R). If R is reflexive then we can
-- indeed obtain `f xs ‚äÜ xs` from `xs ‚äÜ ys ‚Üí f xs ‚äÜ ys`. The other
-- direction is only true if R is both reflexive and transitive.
 
module _ {R : REL A B r} where
 
  tail-Sublist : Sublist R as bs ‚Üí
                 Maybe.All (Œª as ‚Üí Sublist R as bs) (tail as)
  tail-Sublist []        = nothing
  tail-Sublist (b ‚à∑ ≥ ps) = Maybe.map (b ‚à∑ ≥_) (tail-Sublist ps)
  tail-Sublist (p ‚à∑ ps)  = just (_ ‚à∑ ≥ ps)
 
  take-Sublist : ‚àÄ n ‚Üí Sublist R as bs ‚Üí Sublist R (take n as) bs
  take-Sublist n       (y ‚à∑ ≥ rs) = y ‚à∑ ≥ take-Sublist n rs
  take-Sublist zero    rs        = minimum _
  take-Sublist (suc n) []        = []
  take-Sublist (suc n) (r ‚à∑ rs)  = r ‚à∑ take-Sublist n rs
 
  drop-Sublist : ‚àÄ n ‚Üí Sublist R ‚áí (Sublist R ‚àò‚Ä≤ drop n)
  drop-Sublist n       (y ‚à∑ ≥ rs) = y ‚à∑ ≥ drop-Sublist n rs
  drop-Sublist zero    rs        = rs
  drop-Sublist (suc n) []        = []
  drop-Sublist (suc n) (r ‚à∑ rs)  = _ ‚à∑ ≥ drop-Sublist n rs
 
module _ {R : REL A B r} {P : Pred A p} (P? : U.Decidable P) where
 
  takeWhile-Sublist : Sublist R as bs ‚Üí Sublist R (takeWhile P? as) bs
  takeWhile-Sublist []        = []
  takeWhile-Sublist (y ‚à∑ ≥ rs) = y ‚à∑ ≥ takeWhile-Sublist rs
  takeWhile-Sublist {a ‚à∑ as} (r ‚à∑ rs) with does (P? a)
  ... | true  = r ‚à∑ takeWhile-Sublist rs
  ... | false = minimum _
 
  dropWhile-Sublist : Sublist R as bs ‚Üí Sublist R (dropWhile P? as) bs
  dropWhile-Sublist []        = []
  dropWhile-Sublist (y ‚à∑ ≥ rs) = y ‚à∑ ≥ dropWhile-Sublist rs
  dropWhile-Sublist {a ‚à∑ as} (r ‚à∑ rs) with does (P? a)
  ... | true  = _ ‚à∑ ≥ dropWhile-Sublist rs
  ... | false = r ‚à∑ rs
 
  filter-Sublist : Sublist R as bs ‚Üí Sublist R (filter P? as) bs
  filter-Sublist []        = []
  filter-Sublist (y ‚à∑ ≥ rs) = y ‚à∑ ≥ filter-Sublist rs
  filter-Sublist {a ‚à∑ as} (r ‚à∑ rs) with does (P? a)
  ... | true  = r ‚à∑ filter-Sublist rs
  ... | false = _ ‚à∑ ≥ filter-Sublist rs

-- _‚à∑_
 
  ‚à∑À°‚Åª : Sublist R (x ‚à∑ xs) ys ‚Üí Sublist R xs ys
  ‚à∑À°‚Åª (y ‚à∑ ≥ rs) = y ‚à∑ ≥ ‚à∑À°‚Åª rs
  ‚à∑À°‚Åª (r ‚à∑  rs) = _ ‚à∑ ≥ rs
 
  ‚à∑ ≥‚Åª : ¬¨ R x y ‚Üí Sublist R (x ‚à∑ xs) (y ‚à∑ ys) ‚Üí
        Sublist R (x ‚à∑ xs) ys
  ‚à∑ ≥‚Åª ¬¨r (y ‚à∑ ≥ rs) = rs

  ‚à∑‚Åª (y ‚à∑ ≥ rs) = ‚à∑À°‚Åª rs
  ‚à∑‚Åª (x ‚à∑  rs) = rs

-- map
 
  map‚Å∫ : (f : A ‚Üí C) (g : B ‚Üí D) ‚Üí
         Sublist (Œª a b ‚Üí R (f a) (g b)) as bs ‚Üí

  map‚Å∫ f g (r ‚à∑ rs)  = r ‚à∑ map‚Å∫ f g rs

-- _++_
 
  ++‚Å∫ : Sublist R as bs ‚Üí Sublist R cs ds ‚Üí
        Sublist R (as ++ cs) (bs ++ ds)
  ++‚Å∫ []         cds = cds
  ++‚Å∫ (y ‚à∑ ≥ abs) cds = y ‚à∑ ≥ ++‚Å∫ abs cds
  ++‚Å∫ (ab ‚à∑ abs) cds = ab ‚à∑ ++‚Å∫ abs cds

        Sublist R (as ++ cs) (bs ++ ds) ‚Üí Sublist R cs ds
  ++‚Åª {as = []}     {[]}     eq rs = rs
  ++‚Åª {as = a ‚à∑ as} {b ‚à∑ bs} eq rs = ++‚Åª (‚Ñï.suc-injective eq) (‚à∑‚Åª rs)

  ++ ≥ cs []        = minimum cs
  ++ ≥ cs (y ‚à∑ ≥ rs) = y ‚à∑ ≥ ++ ≥ cs rs

-- take / drop
 
  take‚Å∫ : m ‚â§ n ‚Üí Pointwise R as bs ‚Üí
          Sublist R (take m as) (take n bs)
  take‚Å∫ z‚â§n       ps        = minimum _
  take‚Å∫ (s‚â§s m‚â§n) []        = []
  take‚Å∫ (s‚â§s m‚â§n) (p ‚à∑  ps) = p ‚à∑ take‚Å∫ m‚â§n ps
 
  drop‚Å∫ : m ‚â• n ‚Üí Sublist R as bs ‚Üí

  drop‚Å∫ (z‚â§n {m}) rs        = drop-Sublist m rs
  drop‚Å∫ (s‚â§s m‚â•n) []        = []
  drop‚Å∫ (s‚â§s m‚â•n) (y ‚à∑ ≥ rs) = drop‚Å∫ (‚Ñï.m‚â§n‚áím‚â§1+n m‚â•n) rs
  drop‚Å∫ (s‚â§s m‚â•n) (r ‚à∑ rs)  = drop‚Å∫ m‚â•n rs

            Sublist R (drop m as) (drop n bs)

  drop‚Å∫-‚äÜ : ‚àÄ m ‚Üí Sublist R as bs ‚Üí
            Sublist R (drop m as) (drop m bs)
  drop‚Å∫-‚äÜ m = drop‚Å∫ (‚Ñï.‚â§-refl {m})
 
module _ {R : REL A B r} {P : Pred A p} {Q : Pred B q}
         (P? : U.Decidable P) (Q? : U.Decidable Q) where
 
  ‚äÜ-takeWhile-Sublist : (‚àÄ {a b} ‚Üí R a b ‚Üí P a ‚Üí Q b) ‚Üí
                        Pointwise R as bs ‚Üí
                        Sublist R (takeWhile P? as) (takeWhile Q? bs)
  ‚äÜ-takeWhile-Sublist rp‚áíq [] = []
  ‚äÜ-takeWhile-Sublist {a ‚à∑ as} {b ‚à∑ bs} rp‚áíq (p ‚à∑ ps) with P? a | Q? b
  ... | false because _ | _               = minimum _
  ... | true  because _ | true  because _ = p ‚à∑ ‚äÜ-takeWhile-Sublist rp‚áíq ps
  ... | yes pa          | no ¬¨qb          = contradiction (rp‚áíq p pa) ¬¨qb
 
  ‚äá-dropWhile-Sublist : (‚àÄ {a b} ‚Üí R a b ‚Üí Q b ‚Üí P a) ‚Üí
                        Pointwise R as bs ‚Üí
                        Sublist R (dropWhile P? as) (dropWhile Q? bs)
  ‚äá-dropWhile-Sublist rq‚áíp [] = []
  ‚äá-dropWhile-Sublist {a ‚à∑ as} {b ‚à∑ bs} rq‚áíp (p ‚à∑ ps) with P? a | Q? b
  ... | true  because _ | true  because _ = ‚äá-dropWhile-Sublist rq‚áíp ps
  ... | true  because _ | false because _ =
    b ‚à∑ ≥ dropWhile-Sublist P? (fromPointwise ps)
  ... | false because _ | false because _ = p ‚à∑ fromPointwise ps
  ... | no ¬¨pa          | yes qb          = contradiction (rq‚áíp p qb) ¬¨pa
 
  ‚äÜ-filter-Sublist : (‚àÄ {a b} ‚Üí R a b ‚Üí P a ‚Üí Q b) ‚Üí
                     Sublist R as bs ‚Üí Sublist R (filter P? as) (filter Q? bs)
  ‚äÜ-filter-Sublist rp‚áíq [] = []
  ‚äÜ-filter-Sublist rp‚áíq (y ‚à∑ ≥ rs) with does (Q? y)
  ... | true  = y ‚à∑ ≥ ‚äÜ-filter-Sublist rp‚áíq rs
  ... | false = ‚äÜ-filter-Sublist rp‚áíq rs
  ‚äÜ-filter-Sublist {a ‚à∑ as} {b ‚à∑ bs} rp‚áíq (r ‚à∑ rs) with P? a | Q? b
  ... | true  because _ | true  because _ = r ‚à∑ ‚äÜ-filter-Sublist rp‚áíq rs
  ... | false because _ | true  because _ = _ ‚à∑ ≥ ‚äÜ-filter-Sublist rp‚áíq rs
  ... | false because _ | false because _ = ‚äÜ-filter-Sublist rp‚áíq rs
  ... | yes pa          | no ¬¨qb          = contradiction (rp‚áíq r pa) ¬¨qb
 
module _ {R : Rel A r} {P : Pred A p} (P? : U.Decidable P) where
 
  takeWhile-filter : Pointwise R as as ‚Üí
                     Sublist R (takeWhile P? as) (filter P? as)
  takeWhile-filter [] = []
  takeWhile-filter {a ‚à∑ as} (p ‚à∑ ps) with does (P? a)
  ... | true  = p ‚à∑ takeWhile-filter ps
  ... | false = minimum _

  ... | true  = p ‚à∑ filter-Sublist P? (fromPointwise ps)

module _ {R : REL A B r} where

  reverse‚Åª : Sublist R (reverse as) (reverse bs) ‚Üí Sublist R as bs
  reverse‚Åª {as = as} {bs = bs} p = cast (reverse‚Å∫ p) where
    cast = ‚â°.subst‚ÇÇ (Sublist R) (List.reverse-involutive as) (List.reverse-involutive bs)

-- (to/from)Any is a bijection
 
  toAny-injective :{p q : Sublist R [ x ] xs} ‚Üí toAny p ‚â° toAny q ‚Üí p ‚â° q
  toAny-injective {p = y ‚à∑ ≥ p} {y ‚à∑ ≥ q} =

  fromAny-injective : {p q : Any (R x) xs} ‚Üí

  fromAny-injective {p = here px} {here qx} = ‚â°.cong here ‚àò‚Ä≤ ‚à∑-injectiveÀ°
  fromAny-injective {p = there p} {there q} =
    ‚â°.cong there ‚àò‚Ä≤ fromAny-injective ‚àò‚Ä≤ ‚à∑ ≥-injective
 
  toAny‚àòfromAny‚âóid : (p : Any (R x) xs) ‚Üí toAny (fromAny {R = R} p) ‚â° p
  toAny‚àòfromAny‚âóid (here px) = ‚â°.refl
  toAny‚àòfromAny‚âóid (there p) = ‚â°.cong there (toAny‚àòfromAny‚âóid p)
 
  Sublist-[x]-bijection : (Sublist R [ x ] xs) ‚§ñ (Any (R x) xs)
  Sublist-[x]-bijection = mk‚§ñ (toAny-injective , strictlySurjective‚áísurjective < fromAny , toAny‚àòfromAny‚âóid >)

module Reflexivity
    {R : Rel A r}
    (R-refl : Reflexive R) where
 
  reflexive : _‚â°_ ‚áí Sublist R
  reflexive ‚â°.refl = fromPointwise (Pw.refl R-refl)
 
  refl : Reflexive (Sublist R)
  refl = reflexive ‚â°.refl

module Transitivity
    {R : REL A B r} {S : REL B C s} {T : REL A C t}
    (rs‚áít : Trans R S T) where
 
  trans : Trans (Sublist R) (Sublist S) (Sublist T)
  trans rs        (y ‚à∑ ≥ ss) = y ‚à∑ ≥ trans rs ss
  trans (y ‚à∑ ≥ rs) (s ‚à∑ ss)  = _ ‚à∑ ≥ trans rs ss
  trans (r ‚à∑ rs)  (s ‚à∑ ss)  = rs‚áít r s ‚à∑ trans rs ss
  trans []        []        = []
 
open Transitivity public
 
module Antisymmetry
    {R : REL A B r} {S : REL B A s} {E : REL A B e}
    (rs‚áíe : Antisym R S E) where
 
  open ‚Ñï.‚â§-Reasoning
 
  antisym : Antisym (Sublist R) (Sublist S) (Pointwise E)
  antisym []        []        = []
  antisym (r ‚à∑ rs)  (s ‚à∑ ss)  = rs‚áíe r s ‚à∑ antisym rs ss
  -- impossible cases
  antisym (_‚à∑ ≥_ {xs} {ys‚ÇÅ} y rs) (_‚à∑ ≥_ {ys‚ÇÇ} {zs} z ss) =
    contradiction (begin
    length (y ‚à∑ ys‚ÇÅ) ‚â§‚ü® length-mono-‚â§ ss ‚ü©
    length zs        ‚â§‚ü® ‚Ñï.n‚â§1+n (length zs) ‚ü©
    length (z ‚à∑ zs)  ‚â§‚ü® length-mono-‚â§ rs ‚ü©
    length ys‚ÇÅ       ‚àé) $ ‚Ñï.<-irrefl ‚â°.refl
  antisym (_‚à∑ ≥_ {xs} {ys‚ÇÅ} y rs) (_‚à∑_ {y} {ys‚ÇÇ} {z} {zs} s ss)  =
    contradiction (begin
    length (z ‚à∑ zs) ‚â§‚ü® length-mono-‚â§ rs ‚ü©
    length ys‚ÇÅ      ‚â§‚ü® length-mono-‚â§ ss ‚ü©
    length zs       ‚àé) $ ‚Ñï.<-irrefl ‚â°.refl
  antisym (_‚à∑_ {x} {xs} {y} {ys‚ÇÅ} r rs)  (_‚à∑ ≥_ {ys‚ÇÇ} {zs} z ss) =
    contradiction (begin
    length (y ‚à∑ ys‚ÇÅ) ‚â§‚ü® length-mono-‚â§ ss ‚ü©
    length xs        ‚â§‚ü® length-mono-‚â§ rs ‚ü©
    length ys‚ÇÅ       ‚àé) $ ‚Ñï.<-irrefl ‚â°.refl
 
open Antisymmetry public
 
module _ {R : REL A B r} (R? : Decidable R) where
 
  sublist? : Decidable (Sublist R)
  sublist? []       ys       = yes (minimum ys)
  sublist? (x ‚à∑ xs) []       = no Œª ()
  sublist? (x ‚à∑ xs) (y ‚à∑ ys) with R? x y
  ... | true  because  [r] =
    Dec.map (‚à∑‚Åª¬π  (invert  [r])) (sublist? xs ys)
  ... | false because [¬¨r] =
    Dec.map (‚à∑ ≥‚Åª¬π (invert [¬¨r])) (sublist? (x ‚à∑ xs) ys)
 
module _ {E : Rel A e} {R : Rel A r} where
 
  isPreorder : IsPreorder E R ‚Üí IsPreorder (Pointwise E) (Sublist R)
  isPreorder ER-isPreorder = record
    { isEquivalence = Pw.isEquivalence       ER.isEquivalence
    ; reflexive     = fromPointwise ‚àò Pw.map ER.reflexive
    ; trans         = trans                  ER.trans
    } where module ER = IsPreorder ER-isPreorder
 
  isPartialOrder : IsPartialOrder E R ‚Üí IsPartialOrder (Pointwise E) (Sublist R)
  isPartialOrder ER-isPartialOrder = record
    { isPreorder = isPreorder ER.isPreorder
    ; antisym    = antisym    ER.antisym
    } where module ER = IsPartialOrder ER-isPartialOrder
 
  isDecPartialOrder : IsDecPartialOrder E R ‚Üí
                      IsDecPartialOrder (Pointwise E) (Sublist R)
  isDecPartialOrder ER-isDecPartialOrder = record
    { isPartialOrder = isPartialOrder ER.isPartialOrder
    ; _‚âü_            = Pw.decidable   ER._‚âü_
    ; _‚â§?_           = sublist?       ER._‚â§?_
    } where module ER = IsDecPartialOrder ER-isDecPartialOrder
 
preorder : Preorder a e r ‚Üí Preorder _ _ _
preorder ER-preorder = record
  { isPreorder = isPreorder ER.isPreorder
  } where module ER = Preorder ER-preorder
 
poset : Poset a e r ‚Üí Poset _ _ _
poset ER-poset = record
  { isPartialOrder = isPartialOrder ER.isPartialOrder
  } where module ER = Poset ER-poset
 
decPoset : DecPoset a e r ‚Üí DecPoset _ _ _
decPoset ER-poset = record
  { isDecPartialOrder = isDecPartialOrder ER.isDecPartialOrder
  } where module ER = DecPoset ER-poset

-- Properties of disjoint sublists
 
module Disjointness {a b r} {A : Set a} {B : Set b} {R : REL A B r} where
 
  private
    infix 4 _‚äÜ_
    _‚äÜ_ = Sublist R
 
  -- Forgetting the union
 
  DisjointUnion‚ÜíDisjoint : ‚àÄ {xs ys zs us} {œÑ‚ÇÅ : xs ‚äÜ zs} {œÑ‚ÇÇ : ys ‚äÜ zs} {œÑ : us ‚äÜ zs} ‚Üí
    DisjointUnion œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ œÑ ‚Üí Disjoint œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ
  DisjointUnion‚ÜíDisjoint []         = []
  DisjointUnion‚ÜíDisjoint (y   ‚à∑‚Çô u) = y   ‚à∑‚Çô DisjointUnion‚ÜíDisjoint u
  DisjointUnion‚ÜíDisjoint (x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó u) = x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó DisjointUnion‚ÜíDisjoint u
  DisjointUnion‚ÜíDisjoint (x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£ u) = x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£ DisjointUnion‚ÜíDisjoint u
 
  -- Reconstructing the union
 
  Disjoint‚ÜíDisjointUnion : ‚àÄ {xs ys zs} {œÑ‚ÇÅ : xs ‚äÜ zs} {œÑ‚ÇÇ : ys ‚äÜ zs} ‚Üí
    Disjoint œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ ‚Üí ‚àÉ‚ÇÇ Œª us (œÑ : us ‚äÜ zs) ‚Üí DisjointUnion œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ œÑ
  Disjoint‚ÜíDisjointUnion []         = _ , _ , []
  Disjoint‚ÜíDisjointUnion (y   ‚à∑‚Çô u) = _ , _ , y   ‚à∑‚Çô proj‚ÇÇ (proj‚ÇÇ (Disjoint‚ÜíDisjointUnion u))
  Disjoint‚ÜíDisjointUnion (x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó u) = _ , _ , x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó proj‚ÇÇ (proj‚ÇÇ (Disjoint‚ÜíDisjointUnion u))
  Disjoint‚ÜíDisjointUnion (x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£ u) = _ , _ , x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£ proj‚ÇÇ (proj‚ÇÇ (Disjoint‚ÜíDisjointUnion u))
 
  -- Disjoint is decidable
 
  ‚äÜ-disjoint? : ‚àÄ {xs ys zs} (œÑ‚ÇÅ : xs ‚äÜ zs) (œÑ‚ÇÇ : ys ‚äÜ zs) ‚Üí Dec (Disjoint œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ)
  ‚äÜ-disjoint? [] [] = yes []
  -- Present in both sublists: not disjoint.
  ‚äÜ-disjoint? (x‚âàz ‚à∑ œÑ‚ÇÅ) (y‚âàz ‚à∑ œÑ‚ÇÇ) = no Œª()
  -- Present in either sublist: ok.
  ‚äÜ-disjoint? (y ‚à∑ ≥ œÑ‚ÇÅ) (x‚âày ‚à∑ œÑ‚ÇÇ) =
    Dec.map‚Ä≤ (x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£_) (Œª{ (_ ‚à∑·µ£ d) ‚Üí d }) (‚äÜ-disjoint? œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ)
  ‚äÜ-disjoint? (x‚âày ‚à∑ œÑ‚ÇÅ) (y ‚à∑ ≥ œÑ‚ÇÇ) =
    Dec.map‚Ä≤ (x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó_) (Œª{ (_ ‚à∑‚Çó d) ‚Üí d }) (‚äÜ-disjoint? œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ)
  -- Present in neither sublist: ok.
  ‚äÜ-disjoint? (y ‚à∑ ≥ œÑ‚ÇÅ) (.y ‚à∑ ≥ œÑ‚ÇÇ) =
    Dec.map‚Ä≤ (y ‚à∑‚Çô_) (Œª{ (_ ‚à∑‚Çô d) ‚Üí d }) (‚äÜ-disjoint? œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ)
 
  -- Disjoint is proof-irrelevant
 
  Disjoint-irrelevant : ‚àÄ{xs ys zs} ‚Üí Irrelevant (Disjoint {R = R} {xs} {ys} {zs})
  Disjoint-irrelevant [] [] = ‚â°.refl
  Disjoint-irrelevant (y   ‚à∑‚Çô d‚ÇÅ) (.y   ‚à∑‚Çô d‚ÇÇ) = ‚â°.cong (y ‚à∑‚Çô_) (Disjoint-irrelevant d‚ÇÅ d‚ÇÇ)
  Disjoint-irrelevant (x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó d‚ÇÅ) (.x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó d‚ÇÇ) = ‚â°.cong (x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó_) (Disjoint-irrelevant d‚ÇÅ d‚ÇÇ)
  Disjoint-irrelevant (x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£ d‚ÇÅ) (.x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£ d‚ÇÇ) = ‚â°.cong (x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£_) (Disjoint-irrelevant d‚ÇÅ d‚ÇÇ)
 
  -- Note: DisjointUnion is not proof-irrelevant unless the underlying relation R is.
  -- The proof is not entirely trivial, thus, we leave it for future work:
  --
  -- DisjointUnion-irrelevant : Irrelevant R ‚Üí
  --                            ‚àÄ{xs ys us zs} {œÑ : us ‚äÜ zs} ‚Üí
  --                            Irrelevant (Œª (œÑ‚ÇÅ : xs ‚äÜ zs) (œÑ‚ÇÇ : ys ‚äÜ zs) ‚Üí DisjointUnion œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ œÑ)
 
  -- Irreflexivity
 
  Disjoint-irrefl‚Ä≤ : ‚àÄ{xs ys} {œÑ : xs ‚äÜ ys} ‚Üí Disjoint œÑ œÑ ‚Üí Null xs
  Disjoint-irrefl‚Ä≤ []       = []
  Disjoint-irrefl‚Ä≤ (y ‚à∑‚Çô d) = Disjoint-irrefl‚Ä≤ d
 
  Disjoint-irrefl : ‚àÄ{x xs ys} ‚Üí Irreflexive {A = x ‚à∑ xs ‚äÜ ys } _‚â°_ Disjoint
  Disjoint-irrefl ‚â°.refl x with Disjoint-irrefl‚Ä≤ x
  ... | () ‚à∑ _
 
  -- Symmetry
 
  DisjointUnion-sym : ‚àÄ {xs ys xys} {zs} {œÑ‚ÇÅ : xs ‚äÜ zs} {œÑ‚ÇÇ : ys ‚äÜ zs} {œÑ : xys ‚äÜ zs} ‚Üí
                            DisjointUnion œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ œÑ ‚Üí DisjointUnion œÑ‚ÇÇ œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ
  DisjointUnion-sym []         = []
  DisjointUnion-sym (y   ‚à∑‚Çô d) = y ‚à∑‚Çô DisjointUnion-sym d
  DisjointUnion-sym (x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó d) = x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£ DisjointUnion-sym d
  DisjointUnion-sym (x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£ d) = x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó DisjointUnion-sym d
 
  Disjoint-sym : ‚àÄ {xs ys} {zs} {œÑ‚ÇÅ : xs ‚äÜ zs} {œÑ‚ÇÇ : ys ‚äÜ zs} ‚Üí
                 Disjoint œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ ‚Üí Disjoint œÑ‚ÇÇ œÑ‚ÇÅ
  Disjoint-sym []         = []
  Disjoint-sym (y   ‚à∑‚Çô d) = y ‚à∑‚Çô Disjoint-sym d
  Disjoint-sym (x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó d) = x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£ Disjoint-sym d
  Disjoint-sym (x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£ d) = x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó Disjoint-sym d
 
  -- Empty sublist
 
  DisjointUnion-[]À° : ‚àÄ{xs ys} {Œµ : [] ‚äÜ ys} {œÑ : xs ‚äÜ ys} ‚Üí DisjointUnion Œµ œÑ œÑ
  DisjointUnion-[]À° {Œµ = []}     {œÑ = []} = []
  DisjointUnion-[]À° {Œµ = y ‚à∑ ≥ Œµ} {œÑ = y  ‚à∑ ≥ œÑ} = y   ‚à∑‚Çô DisjointUnion-[]À°
  DisjointUnion-[]À° {Œµ = y ‚à∑ ≥ Œµ} {œÑ = x‚âày ‚à∑ œÑ} = x‚âày ‚à∑·µ£ DisjointUnion-[]À°
 
  DisjointUnion-[] ≥ : ‚àÄ{xs ys} {Œµ : [] ‚äÜ ys} {œÑ : xs ‚äÜ ys} ‚Üí DisjointUnion œÑ Œµ œÑ
  DisjointUnion-[] ≥ {Œµ = []}     {œÑ = []} = []
  DisjointUnion-[] ≥ {Œµ = y ‚à∑ ≥ Œµ} {œÑ = y  ‚à∑ ≥ œÑ} = y   ‚à∑‚Çô DisjointUnion-[] ≥
  DisjointUnion-[] ≥ {Œµ = y ‚à∑ ≥ Œµ} {œÑ = x‚âày ‚à∑ œÑ} = x‚âày ‚à∑‚Çó DisjointUnion-[] ≥

  -- [x] ‚äÜ ys (canonical choice) and (‚à∑À°‚Åª œÑ) : xs ‚äÜ ys.
 
  DisjointUnion-fromAny‚àòtoAny-‚à∑À°‚Åª : ‚àÄ {x xs ys} (œÑ : (x ‚à∑ xs) ‚äÜ ys) ‚Üí DisjointUnion (fromAny (toAny œÑ)) (‚à∑À°‚Åª œÑ) œÑ

  DisjointUnion-fromAny‚àòtoAny-‚à∑À°‚Åª (xRy ‚à∑ œÑ) = xRy ‚à∑‚Çó DisjointUnion-[]À°
 
  -- Disjoint union of three mutually disjoint lists.
  --

  record DisjointUnion¬≥

    ; join‚ÇÉ = xRy ‚à∑·µ£ d‚ÇÉ
    }
 
  -- Adding an element to the third list.
 
  _‚à∑‚ÇÉ-DisjointUnion¬≥_ :
    ‚àÄ {xs ys zs ts} {œÑ‚ÇÅ : xs ‚äÜ ts} {œÑ‚ÇÇ : ys ‚äÜ ts} {œÑ‚ÇÉ : zs ‚äÜ ts} ‚Üí

  disjointUnion¬≥ : ‚àÄ{xs ys zs ts} {œÑ‚ÇÅ : xs ‚äÜ ts} {œÑ‚ÇÇ : ys ‚äÜ ts} {œÑ‚ÇÉ : zs ‚äÜ ts}

  -- If a sublist œÑ is disjoint to two lists œÉ‚ÇÅ and œÉ‚ÇÇ,
  -- then also to their disjoint union œÉ.
 
  disjoint‚áídisjoint-to-union : ‚àÄ{xs ys zs yzs ts}

-- Monotonicity of disjointness.
 
module DisjointnessMonotonicity
    {R : REL A B r} {S : REL B C s} {T : REL A C t}
    (rs‚áít : Trans R S T) where
 
  -- We can enlarge and convert the target list of a disjoint union.
 
  weakenDisjointUnion : ‚àÄ {xs ys xys zs ws}
    {œÑ‚ÇÅ : Sublist R xs zs}
    {œÑ‚ÇÇ : Sublist R ys zs}
    {œÑ : Sublist R xys zs} (œÉ : Sublist S zs ws) ‚Üí
    DisjointUnion œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ œÑ ‚Üí
    DisjointUnion (trans rs‚áít œÑ‚ÇÅ œÉ) (trans rs‚áít œÑ‚ÇÇ œÉ) (trans rs‚áít œÑ œÉ)
  weakenDisjointUnion [] [] = []
  weakenDisjointUnion (w  ‚à∑ ≥ œÉ) d         = w ‚à∑‚Çô weakenDisjointUnion œÉ d
  weakenDisjointUnion (_   ‚à∑ œÉ) (y   ‚à∑‚Çô d) = _ ‚à∑‚Çô weakenDisjointUnion œÉ d
  weakenDisjointUnion (zSw ‚à∑ œÉ) (xRz ‚à∑‚Çó d) = rs‚áít xRz zSw ‚à∑‚Çó weakenDisjointUnion œÉ d
  weakenDisjointUnion (zSw ‚à∑ œÉ) (yRz ‚à∑·µ£ d) = rs‚áít yRz zSw ‚à∑·µ£ weakenDisjointUnion œÉ d
 
  weakenDisjoint : ‚àÄ {xs ys zs ws}
    {œÑ‚ÇÅ : Sublist R xs zs}
    {œÑ‚ÇÇ : Sublist R ys zs} (œÉ : Sublist S zs ws) ‚Üí
    Disjoint œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ ‚Üí
    Disjoint (trans rs‚áít œÑ‚ÇÅ œÉ) (trans rs‚áít œÑ‚ÇÇ œÉ)
  weakenDisjoint [] [] = []
  weakenDisjoint (w  ‚à∑ ≥ œÉ) d         = w ‚à∑‚Çô weakenDisjoint œÉ d
  weakenDisjoint (_   ‚à∑ œÉ) (y   ‚à∑‚Çô d) = _ ‚à∑‚Çô weakenDisjoint œÉ d
  weakenDisjoint (zSw ‚à∑ œÉ) (xRz ‚à∑‚Çó d) = rs‚áít xRz zSw ‚à∑‚Çó weakenDisjoint œÉ d
  weakenDisjoint (zSw ‚à∑ œÉ) (yRz ‚à∑·µ£ d) = rs‚áít yRz zSw ‚à∑·µ£ weakenDisjoint œÉ d
 
  -- Lists remain disjoint when elements are removed.
 
  shrinkDisjoint : ‚àÄ {us vs xs ys zs}
                      (œÉ‚ÇÅ : Sublist R us xs) {œÑ‚ÇÅ : Sublist S xs zs}
                      (œÉ‚ÇÇ : Sublist R vs ys) {œÑ‚ÇÇ : Sublist S ys zs} ‚Üí
                      Disjoint œÑ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÇ ‚Üí
                      Disjoint (trans rs‚áít œÉ‚ÇÅ œÑ‚ÇÅ) (trans rs‚áít œÉ‚ÇÇ œÑ‚ÇÇ)
  shrinkDisjoint œÉ‚ÇÅ         œÉ‚ÇÇ (y   ‚à∑‚Çô d) = y ‚à∑‚Çô shrinkDisjoint œÉ‚ÇÅ œÉ‚ÇÇ d
  shrinkDisjoint (x  ‚à∑ ≥ œÉ‚ÇÅ) œÉ‚ÇÇ (xSz ‚à∑‚Çó d) = _ ‚à∑‚Çô shrinkDisjoint œÉ‚ÇÅ œÉ‚ÇÇ d
  shrinkDisjoint (uRx ‚à∑ œÉ‚ÇÅ) œÉ‚ÇÇ (xSz ‚à∑‚Çó d) = rs‚áít uRx xSz ‚à∑‚Çó shrinkDisjoint œÉ‚ÇÅ œÉ‚ÇÇ d
  shrinkDisjoint œÉ‚ÇÅ (y  ‚à∑ ≥ œÉ‚ÇÇ) (ySz ‚à∑·µ£ d) = _ ‚à∑‚Çô shrinkDisjoint œÉ‚ÇÅ œÉ‚ÇÇ d
  shrinkDisjoint œÉ‚ÇÅ (vRy ‚à∑ œÉ‚ÇÇ) (ySz ‚à∑·µ£ d) = rs‚áít vRy ySz ‚à∑·µ£ shrinkDisjoint œÉ‚ÇÅ œÉ‚ÇÇ d
  shrinkDisjoint [] []         []         = []
